      "EN": "Learning is a complex process. It consists of several phases, such as understanding, assimilating, memorizing, analyzing and processing information, and finally confronting it with practice. The value expressed through the QNAD dimension is a probability that describes your degree of autonomy to carry out an effective and sustained learning process. It also allows to predict the type and frequency of interventions that would be useful to you in order to increase your learning capacity",
