    "mainDefinition": {
      "PL": "Podsumowanie zespo\u0142u w wymiarze osobistej identyfikacji z zadaniami, gotowo\u015bci do ponoszenia koszt\u00f3w, sp\u0119dzania czasu, wydatkowania energii w prac\u0119. Ten wymiar dotyczy tak\u017ce tego, czy zesp\u00f3\u0142 b\u0119dzie zdolny do samoistnego wykorzystania w\u0142asnych najlepszych zasob\u00f3w.",
      "EN": "Summary of the team in the dimension of personal identification with tasks, readiness to incur costs, spend time, expenditure of energy at work. This dimension also applies to whether the team will be able to use its own best resources",
      "FR": "R\u00e9sum\u00e9 de l\u2019\u00e9quipe dans la dimension de l\u2019identification personnelle avec les t\u00e2ches, la volont\u00e9 d\u2019engager des co\u00fbts, de passer du temps, de d\u00e9penser de l\u2019\u00e9nergie au travail. Cette dimension s\u2019applique \u00e9galement \u00e0 la question de savoir si l\u2019\u00e9quipe sera en mesure d\u2019utiliser ses propres ressources."
    },
    "lowestDefinition": {
      "PL": "",
      "EN": "",
      "FR": ""
    },
    "highestDefinition": {
      "PL": "",
      "EN": "",
      "FR": ""
    },
    "descriptions": {
      "level_1": {
        "PL": [
          "Niewiele os\u00f3b w zespole deklaruje osobiste zaanga\u017cowanie w r\u00f3\u017cnych sytuacjach, tj. ma\u0142o anga\u017cuje emocji, nie identyfikuj\u0105 si\u0119 z zadaniami, ich spos\u00f3b pracy nie \u015bwiadczy o nich."
        ],
        "EN": [
          "Few people in the team declare personal involvement in various situations, i.e. little engage emotions, do not identify with tasks, their way of working does not testify to them."
        ],
        "FR": [
          "Peu de personnes dans l\u2019\u00e9quipe d\u00e9clarent s\u2019impliquer personnellement dans diverses situations, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire peu engager des \u00e9motions, ne pas s\u2019identifier aux t\u00e2ches, leur fa\u00e7on de travailler ne leur t\u00e9moigne pas."
        ]
      },
      "level_2": {
        "PL": [
          "Cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 os\u00f3b w zespole deklaruje niskie osobiste zaanga\u017cowanie w r\u00f3\u017cnych sytuacjach, tj. ma\u0142o anga\u017cuje emocji, nie identyfikuj\u0105 si\u0119 z zadaniami, ich spos\u00f3b pracy nie \u015bwiadczy o nich."
        ],
        "EN": [
          "Some people in the team declare low personal involvement in various situations, i.e. they do not engage emotions much, they do not identify with the tasks, their way of working does not prove them."
        ],
        "FR": [
          "Certaines personnes de l\u2019\u00e9quipe d\u00e9clarent une faible implication personnelle dans diverses situations, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire qu\u2019elles n\u2019engagent pas beaucoup les \u00e9motions, qu\u2019elles ne s\u2019identifient pas aux t\u00e2ches, que leur fa\u00e7on de travailler ne les prouve pas."
        ]
      },
      "level_3": {
        "PL": [
          "Cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 os\u00f3b w zespole deklaruje osobiste zaanga\u017cowanie w r\u00f3\u017cnych sytuacjach, tj. osobi\u015bcie chce wykona\u0107 prac\u0119 jak najlepiej, identyfikuje si\u0119 z zadaniami, chce odda\u0107 prac\u0119 jak najlepszej jako\u015bci. Cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 os\u00f3b ma\u0142o anga\u017cuje emocji, nie identyfikuj\u0105 si\u0119 z zadaniami, ich spos\u00f3b pracy nie \u015bwiadczy o nich."
        ],
        "EN": [
          "Some people in the team declare personal commitment in various situations, i.e. they personally want to do the best work, identify with the tasks, want to give the work of the best quality. Some people do not engage emotions much, they do not identify with tasks, their way of working does not testify to them."
        ],
        "FR": [
          "Certaines personnes de l\u2019\u00e9quipe d\u00e9clarent un engagement personnel dans diverses situations, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire qu\u2019elles veulent personnellement faire le meilleur travail, s\u2019identifier aux t\u00e2ches, vouloir donner le travail de la meilleure qualit\u00e9. Certaines personnes n\u2019engagent pas beaucoup les \u00e9motions, elles ne s\u2019identifient pas aux t\u00e2ches, leur fa\u00e7on de travailler n\u2019en t\u00e9moigne pas."
        ]
      },
      "level_4": {
        "PL": [
          "Spora cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 os\u00f3b podkre\u015bla, \u017ce identyfikuje si\u0119 z zadaniami, \u017ce osobi\u015bcie zale\u017cy im na dobrej jako\u015bci. Anga\u017cuj\u0105 si\u0119, mobilizuj\u0105 zasoby."
        ],
        "EN": [
          "A lot of people emphasize that they identify with the tasks, that they personally care about good quality. They get involved, they mobilize resources."
        ],
        "FR": [
          "Beaucoup de gens soulignent qu\u2019ils s\u2019identifient aux t\u00e2ches, qu\u2019ils se soucient personnellement de la bonne qualit\u00e9. Ils s\u2019impliquent, ils mobilisent des ressources."
        ]
      },
      "level_5": {
        "PL": [
          "Wi\u0119ksza cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 os\u00f3b podkre\u015bla, \u017ce identyfikuje si\u0119 z zadaniami, \u017ce osobi\u015bcie zale\u017cy im na dobrej jako\u015bci. Anga\u017cuj\u0105 si\u0119, mobilizuj\u0105 zasoby."
        ],
        "EN": [
          "Most people emphasize that they identify with the tasks, that they personally care about good quality. They get involved, they mobilize resources."
        ],
        "FR": [
          "La plupart des gens soulignent qu\u2019ils s\u2019identifient aux t\u00e2ches, qu\u2019ils se soucient personnellement de la bonne qualit\u00e9. Ils s\u2019impliquent, ils mobilisent des ressources."
        ]
      }
    },
