      "EN": "Ability to guide and direct ones' needs and desires, in order to keep moving towards ones' goals with enthusiasm and a positive attitude. People with high scores are able to direct themselves to ensure that they keep progressing forward with their goals. They tend to guide their positive attitude and enthusiasm to facilitate this process. People with low scores may find it difficult to direct themselves towards their goals, as they may lack enthusiasm and drive to reach these goals.",
